root: ^!After waiting in a short line to get in, we finally find ourselves in a small venue with a stage at one end and a bar at the other. Most people here are closer to Amelia’s age than mine. I suddenly feel very out of place.
^!My waning youth is showing. I am suddenly aware of my mortality. When were the good years of my life? Will Amelia still love me as we both grow older? Wait, is seapunk actually a genre?
^!A younger kid runs up and high fives Madi.
